41:05.863 --> 41:10.200
â™ª he'll be there waiting

41:10.202 --> 41:14.237
â™ª for all of your life

41:14.239 --> 41:17.607
â™ª and though our goals are all

41:17.609 --> 41:20.109
â™ª at one

